high_descs: Turn right, then left and walk to the sink in the middle of the counter.
Pick up the fork in the left sink basin.
Turn to your left and face the microwave.
Open the cupboard underneath the microwave and place the fork in the glass in the cupboard.
Pick up the glass with the fork in it.
Turn around and move to face the sink again.
Put down the glass with the fork in it in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a fork in it into the left sink basin.

high_descs: Move forward to the left sink.
Pick up the fork in the left sink.
Turn left, bring the fork to the microwave.  put the fork in the cup sitting in the cabinet under the microwave on the counter.
Put the fork in the cup sitting in the cabinet under the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the cup with fork in the cabinet.
Bring the cup back to the sink on your right.
Put the cup with fork in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with fork in it, in the left sink.

high_descs: walk to face sink
pick up fork from sink
turn left to face microwave
open bottom cabinet door, put fork in glass inside cabinet
pick up glass inside cabinet
turn right to face sink
put glass into the sink
anns.task_desc: put a glass and fork into the kitchen sink
